  <text>
     <body>
     <div type="poem">
   <lg>
      <l>
         <seg rend="decorInit">W</seg>Han faythe fayleth in preestes sawes</l>
      <l>And lordes hestes are holden for lawes</l>
      <l>And robbery is holden purchace</l>
      <l>And lechery is holden solace</l>
      <l>Than shall the londe of Albyon</l>
      <l>Be brought to great confusyon</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>It falleth for euery gentylman</l>
      <l>To saye the best that he can</l>
      <l>In mannes absence</l>
      <l>And the sothe in hys presence</l>
      <l>It cometh by kynde of gentyll blood</l>
      <l>To caste away all heuynesse</l>
      <l>And gader togyder wordes good</l>
      <l>The werke of wysedome beareth wytnesse</l>
   </lg>
   <trailer>FINIS.</trailer>
</div>
